snippet.title: ▲PERFECT STRIDE▲ alpha trailer
snippet.description:
▲▲▲PERFECT STRIDE▲▲▲
http://arcanekids.com
First person maximalist skater for PC & OSX [and tentatively linux!]. Based on old school FPS movement exploits (ala Quake jumping, Tribes skiing, CS surfing). The controls are hella hard & we like it that way.

Get the ALPHA version through LA Game Space when the game pack becomes available
http://lagamespace.org

Game: Ben Esposito (@torahhorse) & Russell Honor (@russellhonor)
Additional FX: Pete Anderson (@dmnddst)

Music by Chromadadata
http://soundcloud.com/chromadadata
